{"sn2.25:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.25 ","sn2.25:0.2":"3. Nanatitthiyavagga ","sn2.25:0.3":"Jantusutta ","sn2.25:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn2.25:1.2":"ekam samayam sambahula bhikkhu, kosalesu viharanti himavantapasse arannakutikaya uddhata unnala capala mukhara vikinnavaca mutthassatino asampajana asamahita vibbhantacitta pakatindriya. ","sn2.25:2.1":"Atha kho jantu devaputto tadahuposathe pannarase yena te bhikkhu tenupasankami; upasankamitva te bhikkhu gathahi ajjhabhasi: ","sn2.25:3.1":"“Sukhajivino pure asum, ","sn2.25:3.2":"bhikkhu gotamasavaka; ","sn2.25:3.3":"Aniccha pindamesana, ","sn2.25:3.4":"aniccha sayanasanam; ","sn2.25:3.5":"Loke aniccatam natva, ","sn2.25:3.6":"dukkhassantam akamsu te. ","sn2.25:4.1":"Dupposam katva attanam, ","sn2.25:4.2":"game gamanika viya; ","sn2.25:4.3":"Bhutva bhutva nipajjanti, ","sn2.25:4.4":"paragaresu mucchita. ","sn2.25:5.1":"Sanghassa anjalim katva, ","sn2.25:5.2":"idhekacce vadamaham; ","sn2.25:5.3":"Apaviddha anatha te, ","sn2.25:5.4":"yatha peta tatheva te. ","sn2.25:6.1":"Ye kho pamatta viharanti, ","sn2.25:6.2":"te me sandhaya bhasitam; ","sn2.25:6.3":"Ye appamatta viharanti, ","sn2.25:6.4":"namo tesam karomahan”ti. "}